OL,6,FAn "infatuated" prison worker who sent
OL,7,Fsexual images to an inmate and had a
OL,8,Fpillow printed with a picture of his
OL,9,Fface has been jailed.
OL,11,FA court heard Nikki Croft, 51, also
OL,12,Fgave the man, who was serving a
OL,13,Fsentence at HMP Morton Hall near
OL,14,FLincoln, 11 illicit SIM cards.
OL,16,FShe admitted misconduct in a public
OL,17,Foffice at Lincoln Crown Court and was
OL,18,Fjailed for a year.
