OL,6,FThe court heard Croft was employed as
OL,7,Fa civilian worker helping inmates with
OL,8,Flearning difficulties at the category
OL,9,FC prison.
OL,11,FDeclan Austin, prosecuting, said Croft
OL,12,Fbecame "infatuated" with the prisoner
OL,13,F- referred to as "LZ" - and started
OL,14,Fspeaking to him in December 2022.
OL,16,FThe court heard rumours began to
OL,17,Fcirculate within the prison about an
OL,18,Finappropriate relationship and Croft
OL,19,Fwas invited to a "challenge meeting"
OL,20,Fon 22 February 2023 but denied any
OL,21,Fwrongdoing.
