OL,6,FShe was suspended until April 2023,
OL,7,Fwhen she was reinstated after the
OL,8,Finvestigation proved inclusive but
OL,9,Fsuspicions were again raised after she
OL,10,Fcontinued to stay in contact with the
OL,11,Fprisoiner.
OL,13,F"She sent photographs of herself to
OL,14,Fhim who by this time was at HMP
OL,15,FLincoln, and were subsequently found
OL,16,Fin his cell," Mr Austin said.
OL,18,F"They were photos of her in sexually
OL,19,Fmotivated positions, in underwear."
