OL,3,C'Infatuated' prisoner worker had
OL,4,Cpillow with inmate's face on
OL,6,FAnother photograph showed Croft with a
OL,7,Fring baring the initials "LZ".
OL,9,FInvestigations revealed phone contact
OL,10,Fbetween the pair and a message from
OL,11,FCroft which read "sick of white men."
OL,13,FCroft, whose address can not be
OL,14,Fdisclosed because of a court order,
OL,15,Fadmitted two charges of misconduct in
OL,16,Fpublic office.
OL,18,FNeil Sands, mitigating, asked the
OL,19,Fcourt to consider why a woman of
OL,20,F"adult years" had succumbed to an
OL,21,Finmate.
